I tend to have a preference for the somewhat quirky SCPs. One thing in particular I don't understand, though, is why they're just leaving their diplomats stranded on the station. Yes, the engines are a part of the anomaly, but so far there's no indication that they haven't worked, and it would seem to me more sensible to use them a last time to evacuate personnel from an unstable location in spacetime, especially if they're looking to contain the reality bender (who might decide to do something quite punitive if he gets upset). The Foundation can't treat its personnel as casually expendable, or they won't have any personnel left.







